{"type":"message","id":"2d0e27c0","parentId":"0e733510","timestamp":"2026-04-05T03:55:40.545Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_E6P3ANDo53tIKBsdouTuGpd2|fc_0083665ee16b82040169d1dd37e6588193bfa92bbc47115b6c","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"== openclaw skills help ==\n\nđŠ OpenClaw 2026.4.2 (d74a122) â I'm not magicâI'm just extremely persistent with retries and coping strategies.\n\nUsage: openclaw skills [options] [command]\n\nList and inspect available skills\n\nOptions:\n  -h, --help  Display help for command\n\nCommands:\n  check       Check which skills are ready vs missing requirements\n  info        Show detailed information about a skill\n  install     Install a skill from ClawHub into the active workspace\n  list        List all available skills\n  search      Search ClawHub skills\n  update      Update ClawHub-installed skills in the active workspace\n\nDocs: https://docs.openclaw.ai/cli/skills\n\n\n== cli skill run help ==\n\nđŠ OpenClaw 2026.4.2 (d74a122) â I can run local, remote, or purely on vibesâresults may vary with DNS.\n\nUsage: openclaw skills [options] [command]\n\nList and inspect available skills\n\nOptions:\n  -h, --help  Display help for command\n\nCommands:\n  check       Check which skills are ready vs missing requirements\n  info        Show detailed information about a skill\n  install     Install a skill from ClawHub into the active workspace\n  list        List all available skills\n  search      Search ClawHub skills\n  update      Update ClawHub-installed skills in the active workspace\n\nDocs: https://docs.openclaw.ai/cli/skills"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":2567,"aggregated":"== openclaw skills help ==\n\nđŠ OpenClaw 2026.4.2 (d74a122) â I'm not magicâI'm just extremely persistent with retries and coping strategies.\n\nUsage: openclaw skills [options] [command]\n\nList and inspect available skills\n\nOptions:\n  -h, --help  Display help for command\n\nCommands:\n  check       Check which skills are ready vs missing requirements\n  info        Show detailed information about a skill\n  install     Install a skill from ClawHub into the active workspace\n  list        List all available skills\n  search      Search ClawHub skills\n  update      Update ClawHub-installed skills in the active workspace\n\nDocs: https://docs.openclaw.ai/cli/skills\n\n\n== cli skill run help ==\n\nđŠ OpenClaw 2026.4.2 (d74a122) â I can run local, remote, or purely on vibesâresults may vary with DNS.\n\nUsage: openclaw skills [options] [command]\n\nList and inspect available skills\n\nOptions:\n  -h, --help  Display help for command\n\nCommands:\n  check       Check which skills are ready vs missing requirements\n  info        Show detailed information about a skill\n  install     Install a skill from ClawHub into the active workspace\n  list        List all available skills\n  search      Search ClawHub skills\n  update      Update ClawHub-installed skills in the active workspace\n\nDocs: https://docs.openclaw.ai/cli/skills","cwd":"/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775361340542}}
{"type":"message","id":"6cb57407","parentId":"2d0e27c0","timestamp":"2026-04-05T03:55:49.632Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"èœèŁăèżäžȘçæŹç `openclaw skills install` ćȘæŻæä» ClawHub ćźèŁïŒäžæŻæçŽæ„âćźèŁ zip æŹć°ćâă  \næä»„æŹć°ćźèŁçæ­ŁçĄźćæłæŻïŒ**æ skill çźćœæŸć°çšæ·æèœçźćœ `~/.openclaw/skills/feishu-bot-manager`**ă\n\nèżäžæ­„æŻäœéŁé©æä»¶ć€ć¶ïŒçæ­ŁçæéćžžèżéèŠ OpenClaw éæ°ćç°æèœïŒćżèŠæ¶ćéćŻæćĄă  \næç°ćšćæćźæŸć°æèœçźćœéïŒćč¶éĄșæć»æćçŒ©ćéç macOS ććŸæä»¶ă","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0083665ee16b82040169d1dd3f0d588193b6a525a670e3b3bf\",\"phase\":\"commentary\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_2EVY04Qkch2L34tTDN3Ufr96|fc_0083665ee16b82040169d1dd41961c8193b8bdaf6afcf2eb01","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"set -e\nTARGET=/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/home/.openclaw/skills/feishu-bot-manager\nSRC=/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/tmp/feishu-bot-manager/feishu-bot-manager\nrm -rf \"$TARGET\"\nmkdir -p \"$TARGET\"\ncp -R \"$SRC\"/. \"$TARGET\"/\nfind \"$TARGET\" -name '.DS_Store' -delete || true\nfind \"$TARGET\" -name '__MACOSX' -type d -prune -exec rm -rf {} + || true\nprintf 'installed to: %s\\n' \"$TARGET\"\nprintf '\\ncontents:\\n'\nfind \"$TARGET\" -maxdepth 2 | sed 's#^#/##' | head -100","workdir":"/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace","yieldMs":10000,"timeout":30},"partialJson":"{\"command\":\"set -e\\nTARGET=/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/home/.openclaw/skills/feishu-bot-manager\\nSRC=/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/tmp/feishu-bot-manager/feishu-bot-manager\\nrm -rf \\\"$TARGET\\\"\\nmkdir -p \\\"$TARGET\\\"\\ncp -R \\\"$SRC\\\"/. \\\"$TARGET\\\"/\\nfind \\\"$TARGET\\\" -name '.DS_Store' -delete || true\\nfind \\\"$TARGET\\\" -name '__MACOSX' -type d -prune -exec rm -rf {} + || true\\nprintf 'installed to: %s\\\\n' \\\"$TARGET\\\"\\nprin