ord|irc|googlechat|slack|signal|imessage|line\n                             (omit to use the main session channel)\n  --deliver                  Send the agent's reply back to the selected channel\n                             (default: false)\n  -h, --help                 Display help for command\n  --json                     Output result as JSON (default: false)\n  --local                    Run the embedded agent locally (requires model\n                             provider API keys in your shell) (default: false)\n  -m, --message <text>       Message body for the agent\n  --reply-account <id>       Delivery account id override\n  --reply-channel <channel>  Delivery channel override (separate from routing)\n  --reply-to <target>        Delivery target override (separate from session\n                             routing)\n  --session-id <id>          Use an explicit session id\n  -t, --to <number>          Recipient number in E.164 used to derive the\n                             session key\n  --thinking <level>         Thinking level: off | minimal | low | medium | high\n                             | xhigh\n  --timeout <seconds>        Override agent command timeout (seconds, default\n                             600 or config value)\n  --verbose <on|off>         Persist agent verbose level for the session\n\nExamples:\n  openclaw agent --to +15555550123 --message \"status update\"\n    Start a new session.\n  openclaw agent --agent ops --message \"Summarize logs\"\n    Use a specific agent.\n  openclaw agent --session-id 1234 --message \"Summarize inbox\" --thinking medium\n    Target a session with explicit thinking level.\n  openclaw agent --to +15555550123 --message \"Trace logs\" --verbose on --json\n    Enable verbose logging and JSON output.\n  openclaw agent --to +15555550123 --message \"Summon reply\" --deliver\n    Deliver reply.\n  openclaw agent --agent ops --message \"Generate report\" --deliver --reply-channel slack --reply-to \"#reports\"\n    Send reply to a different channel/target.\n\nDocs: https://docs.openclaw.ai/cli/agent\n---AGENT DIRS---\n/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/home/.openclaw/agents/main/agent/models.json\n/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/home/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/99398699-10a8-4bad-a270-909315f00b8e.jsonl\n/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/home/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/sessions.json.bak-20260403-230913\n/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/home/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/sessions.json.bak-20260403-230944\n/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/home/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/a23f7374-28cc-448a-9feb-e9dcc903af11.jsonl.reset.2026-04-03T20-00-37.035Z\n/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/home/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/43dcac88-1198-4f4d-bf82-205b8021f756.jsonl\n/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/home/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/0b320bce-db00-4509-98f0-9bf3e457f836.jsonl.reset.2026-04-04T03-07-23.942Z\n/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/home/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/a38e6280-113b-457f-8ccc-7bf172906c72.jsonl.reset.2026-04-04T06-17-52.673Z\n/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/home/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/a91022bd-2ab1-4e8f-acc0-d44e605dd7e4.jsonl\n/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/home/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/3d5daa7e-d8b2-4ad8-beb9-6d683280b5ae.jsonl.reset.2026-04-04T20-41-10.803Z\n/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/home/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/68a1467c-d384-4636-9242-b95a95e32d23.jsonl\n/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/home/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/dbb57fa6-e774-4998-847c-d6e39e9ece68.jsonl.reset.2026-04-05T01-41-09.615Z\n/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/home/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/8d6f31a6-bb8c-4234-9ac3-9ea4978185d6.jsonl\n/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/home/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/d2418bb4-e2cc-4bab-b1af-fe833d634138.jsonl\n/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/home/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/c8e52ef4-808a-45a6-9697-7f1725b78529.jsonl\n/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/home/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/e10a4cb5-4d