{"type":"message","id":"d9db1809","parentId":"230581d0","timestamp":"2026-04-05T13:00:34.034Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_oTlo0QwFECKNKe8wjiyPfy5H|fc_04d4768b795231fd0169d25ce3b430819b864bfd6f795fc15c","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"đŠ OpenClaw 2026.4.2 (d74a122)\n   Easter: I found your missing environment variableâconsider it a tiny CLI egg hunt with fewer jellybeans.\n\nUsage: openclaw agents set-identity [options]\n\nUpdate an agent identity (name/theme/emoji/avatar)\n\nOptions:\n  --agent <id>            Agent id to update\n  --avatar <value>        Identity avatar (workspace path, http(s) URL, or data\n                          URI)\n  --emoji <emoji>         Identity emoji\n  --from-identity         Read values from IDENTITY.md (default: false)\n  -h, --help              Display help for command\n  --identity-file <path>  Explicit IDENTITY.md path to read\n  --json                  Output JSON summary (default: false)\n  --name <name>           Identity name\n  --theme <theme>         Identity theme\n  --workspace <dir>       Workspace directory used to locate the agent +\n                          IDENTITY.md\n\nExamples:\n  openclaw agents set-identity --agent main --name \"OpenClaw\" --emoji \"đŠ\"\n    Set name + emoji.\n  openclaw agents set-identity --agent main --avatar avatars/openclaw.png\n    Set avatar path.\n  openclaw agents set-identity --workspace ~/.openclaw/workspace --from-identity\n    Load from IDENTITY.md.\n  openclaw agents set-identity --identity-file ~/.openclaw/workspace/IDENTITY.md --agent main\n    Use a specific IDENTITY.md."}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":3209,"aggregated":"đŠ OpenClaw 2026.4.2 (d74a122)\n   Easter: I found your missing environment variableâconsider it a tiny CLI egg hunt with fewer jellybeans.\n\nUsage: openclaw agents set-identity [options]\n\nUpdate an agent identity (name/theme/emoji/avatar)\n\nOptions:\n  --agent <id>          